const colors = {
    error: "#EF0024",
    primary: "#18B18D",
    secondary: "#FFE600",
    darkGrey: "#333333",
    lightGrey: "#BBBBBB",
    white: "#fff",
    border: "#dddddd",
    text: "#333",
    superLightGrey: "#eeeeee",
    midGrey: "#888888",
    grey: "#f2f2f2",
    green: "#6FCF97",
};

export default colors;
